              br
              | &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;➜ creating <b style="color:black;">css/js/html/jade/coffeejscript/dart</b> webpages and snippets,
              br
              | &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;➜ overcoming difficulties when it came to use <b style="color:black;">C++ Win API</b> (hungarian notation huh?)
