              | &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;➜ using professional-level <b style="color:black;">ocaml</b> during studies
              br
              | &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;➜ creating xml-understanding <b style="color:black;">java</b> reflection-based frameworks
              br
              | &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;➜ messing things up <b style="color:black;">with V8</b> (this compilation takes forever huh)
              br
              | &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;➜ writing <b style="color:black;">plugins for Atom</b>
              br
              | &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;➜ playing around with <b style="color:black;">Grunt/Node/Webpack</b> and <b style="color:black;">React/Angular</b> stuff
              br
              br
              | <b style="color:black;">And many other things!</b>
              br
              br
              | I'm keen on programming and doing these things for fun.
              br
              | If you actually want to give me a chance and use my potential Just
